  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"DQ5KhiiY\">我不是大佬，所以我一定要用翻译软件！我身边的大佬，基本不用，除了看到一些专业词汇看不懂的时候，会翻一下字典什么的。</p><p data-pid=\"s6K6r-6E\">但是对于普通人来说，外文的文献虽然有很多宝藏，但是直接阅读还是有难度的，借助一些翻译平台，可以让我们更快的获得知识！</p><p data-pid=\"uJRhqELw\">直接给大家推荐几款我和我的朋友用过，感觉还不错的翻译平台吧。</p><p data-pid=\"BlILgZyx\"><b>一、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=609792292&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%A6%8F%E6%98%95&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">福昕<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>翻译</b></p><p data-pid=\"uOmTrceH\">直达链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//fanyi.pdf365.cn/%3Fagent%3Dzhihu\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">fanyi.pdf365.cn/?</span><span class=\"invisible\">agent=zhihu</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"5FTTymw9\">这款是真的推荐过很多次了，因为用起来的感觉不错，而且准确率还挺高的，尤其是对于专业性文件来说， 当然如果是合同什么的，我还是建议大家去找找人工翻译，会更加有保障一点，虽然现在很多人表示AI翻译的比人准确多了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1526\" data-rawheight=\"803\" data-original-token=\"v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba265f51be3391a0ad78dcc594afb74b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1526\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1526' height='803'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1526\" data-rawheight=\"803\" data-original-token=\"v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba265f51be3391a0ad78dcc594afb74b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1526\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-27503e4b355b8b973c64d837d3ae87d9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"JFbEq_gS\">直接导入文字或是文件就可以翻译。甚至连图片都可以哦！</p><p data-pid=\"MVEqLGag\"><b>二、foxit reader</b></p><p data-pid=\"K0khwyI0\">直达链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.foxitsoftware.cn/pdf-reader/%3Fagent%3DzhihuAD\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://www.foxitsoftware.cn/pdf-reader</a></p><p data-pid=\"XSTNDZSF\">这个我主要是用来看<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=609792292&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=PDF%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">PDF格式<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的文件，毕竟现在太多文件都喜欢保存为PDF格式了！用这个软件，还能直接给我识别那种扫描件呢！让我可以阅读和查看更多的PDF文件，根本没在怕的！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1190\" data-rawheight=\"160\" data-original-token=\"v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1190\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1190' height='160'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1190\" data-rawheight=\"160\" data-original-token=\"v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1190\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54b999e7bc7f75a23c7bd6a12ff1f525_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"txdBk0aL\"><b>三、ImTranslator</b></p><p data-pid=\"FChJHIef\">直达链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//imtranslator.net/\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">imtranslator.net/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"9sEUGUiL\">这是一个<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=609792292&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">谷歌<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>插件，我主要是用来浏览网页的时候使用，毕竟谁没有上网的时候遇到看不懂的单词呢。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"600\" data-original-token=\"v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-659fb93a1fb15dec2ab184d708176926_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='600' height='600'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"600\" data-original-token=\"v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-659fb93a1fb15dec2ab184d708176926_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c37b9a852ba833bf915c6e55c5a4fa8d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
